review.reviewBody: The Oaxaca bowl was delicious. It tasted exactly as it was described on the menu. I ordered the special, 241 and will have the second one tomorrow. I will order from them again. ￼

the Mixed Mixed Berrii was not that good. It was very bland. 

the Oaxaca Bowl was great as usual!
It's the second time I ordered extra crispy wontons and got next to zero crispy wontons?

It was my first time trying it with one of my friends and it was delicious! The rice could've been softer to my taste but still very good, I absolutely loved the tropical mango smoothie it had a vanilla mango banana taste. Ive been dying to go back into the store for another smoothie and bowl! 

Follow my instgram: @kashingoutkee
Bowls good but a little dry. Could have used more of the sauce
